headline: 3 Reasons WAT is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Although the S&P 500 is down 1.6% over the past six months, Waters Corporation’s stock price has fallen further to $342.30, losing shareholders 8.5% of their capital. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
